menu "Firmware RE Lab — Configuration"

    config ENABLE_LCD
        bool "Enable ST7735 LCD display"
        default y
        help
            Drive the on-board 0.96" ST7735 LCD.
            Disable to save flash/RAM or if the display is absent.

    config LCD_BACKLIGHT_INVERTED
        bool "LCD backlight is active-low"
        default y
        depends on ENABLE_LCD
        help
            Some T-Dongle-S3 revisions invert the backlight pin.
            Enable if the display stays dark with the default setting.

endmenu
